act1.name: Pickleball
act1.description: Pickleball is a fast-paced paddle sport that combines elements of tennis, badminton, and ping-pong. Players use solid paddles to hit a perforated ball over a net, aiming to score points while engaging in strategic rallies. [INTENSITY: EASY]

act3.name: Basketball
act3.description:
Intensity: hard 
 Basketball is a high-energy team sport played on a rectangular court with hoops positioned at each end. Players aim to score points by shooting a ball through the opponent's hoop while preventing them from doing the same. With its fast-paced gameplay, dribbling, passing, and shooting skills, basketball captivates players and fans worldwide, embodying teamwork, athleticism, and strategy.
